    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to legislators of the United States who are elected to one of the two Houses of Congress as representatives of one of the states or of defined districts within a state.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
